effects.display_string:

Overpower has a 15% chance to end your Winning Streak!
Set: When your Winning Streak! ends you gain 2% Haste and your Mortal Strike and Cleave damage is increased by 2% per stack of Winning Streak! you had for 12 sec.

name: Cyrce's Circlet
description: Sea dogs and tale spinners tell stories of a mythical siren that could lure even the stubbornest sailors to a watery grave.

spells.description:
Use: Channel to vent flames for 2 sec, dealing 2.7 million Fire damage split between all nearby enemies.

Mechanical enemies become Superheated, taking 132,454  additional Fire damage when struck by your next harmful ability. (2 Min Cooldown)

Use: Push the Big Red Button, launching a missile barrage which deals 2.2 million Fire damage split among all enemies in the area. Deals increased damage when striking multiple targets. (2 Min Cooldown)
Use: Teleports the caster to the Argent Tournament Grounds. (30 Min Cooldown)
